#: serverguide/C/web-servers.xml:779(para)
msgid ""
"Modify the <filename>/etc/apache2/sites-available/default</filename> "
"configuration file to setup your domains."
msgstr ""
"Modifiera filen <filename>/etc/apache2/sites-available/default</filename>  "
"för att konfigurera dina domäner."

#: serverguide/C/web-servers.xml:783(para)
msgid ""
"The first thing to change is the <emphasis>DocumentRoot</emphasis> directive:"
msgstr ""
"Den första saken att ändra är <emphasis>DocumentRoot</emphasis> "
"instruktionen:"

#: serverguide/C/web-servers.xml:787(programlisting)
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\n"
"DocumentRoot /path/to/rails/application/public\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"DocumentRoot /path/to/rails/application/public\n"

#: serverguide/C/web-servers.xml:790(para)
msgid ""
"Next, change the &lt;Directory \"/path/to/rails/application/public\"&gt; "
"directive:"
